---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro'
import { SITE_URL } from '../lib/site'
---
<PublicLayout
  title="Disclaimer — DegreeWiki"
  description="DegreeWiki is an independent information platform. Match scores and AI responses are assistive only and do not guarantee any outcome."
  canonical={SITE_URL + '/disclaimer'}
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Disclaimer</h1>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Independence</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        DegreeWiki is an independent education information platform. It is not affiliated with,
        endorsed by, or operated by any university, scholarship organisation, government agency,
        or immigration authority.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Data accuracy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Program details, tuition amounts, deadlines, admission requirements, scholarship
        eligibility, and visa policies change frequently. DegreeWiki makes a reasonable effort
        to keep information up to date, but we cannot guarantee that every page reflects the
        most current official information.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
        Always confirm important details — including tuition, deadlines, eligibility, and
        admission requirements — directly with the official university, scholarship provider,
        or government website before applying.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Fit Finder match scores</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Fit Finder scores show how closely a program matches your saved study preferences.
        A higher score means the program aligns more closely with your saved preferences.
        It does not mean you are likely to be admitted, eligible for scholarships, eligible
        for a visa, or likely to complete the program.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Fit Finder results are <strong>not</strong>:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Admissions assessments</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Eligibility determinations</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Scholarship forecasts</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Visa outcome predictions</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Career or salary guarantees</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">AI features</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        When AI-assisted features are available on DegreeWiki, they are assistive tools to help
        you explore and understand education options. AI responses are based on available
        DegreeWiki context. They are not authoritative, legally binding, or guaranteed to be
        correct or complete. Always verify AI-suggested information with the relevant official
        source.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">No guarantees</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">DegreeWiki does not guarantee:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Admission to any program</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Receipt of any scholarship</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Visa approval</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Employment after graduation</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Any specific salary or career outcome</li>
        <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gray-400 shrink-0">&mdash;</span>Completeness or currentness of any information on this site</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
      <a href="/about"   class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">About</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Privacy</a>
      <a href="/terms"   class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Terms of Use</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</PublicLayout>
